        "show": false,
        "level": 1
      },
      "image": {},
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>This service is unlocked once <strong>Checkered Past</strong> has been completed. It takes place in the gambling pits of the 7th Circle, and is orchestrated by Checkers (or her replacement) along with other Afterlife staff.</p><h3>Cost</h3><p><strong>At least 1 Eagle is the required ante, but more can be offered.</strong> Any player can roll the gambling table once, each day that they pay for entry into the 7th Circle.</p><h3>Function</h3><p>For a certain type of character, the gambling pits at the Afterlife offer a way to make lots of Eagles, very quickly, and provide the following services:</p><ul><li><p><strong>Gamble Your Coins:</strong> There's always <em>some</em> kind of game going in the pit, and they all play with Eagles instead of cash. They're usually the <strong>moderate</strong> difficulty, but can be upped further at GM discretion.</p></li><li><p><strong>Pay Your Debts &amp; Conflict Resolution:</strong> Well-moderated gambling is a good way for players to wriggle out of debt against greedy sharks of all types, or to settle disagreements among themselves. The Afterlife's dealers provide a neutral judge, and cheating is punished. Harshly.</p></li></ul><p></p>"
      },
